-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"CRM"}],["$","span","property management",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"property management"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-goated","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Real estate is a relationship business. A good agent tracks hundreds of prospects, manages property listings, coordinates with brokers, handles paperwork, and somehow remembers to follow up."}]]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Throw them into Salesforce and they are lost. The software feels like it was designed for car salesmen, not real estate professionals. It was."}]]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"This is why smart real estate teams build custom systems or use real estate-specific platforms. And why the ones that do close more deals."}]]}],["$","h2","3",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"What Makes Real Estate Different"}],["$","h3","4",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"1. Relationships span years"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A buyer might express interest in your listings today but not buy for 18 months. You need to nurture that relationship without spamming them."}]]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A seller might list a property, not sell it, list again next year. You need complete history."}]]}],["$","h3","7",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"2. Multiple concurrent transactions"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"One agent might have 5 active buyers, 3 listed properties, 2 past clients they are following up with, and 10 leads in early-stage conversations. Each relationship has its own timeline and urgency."}]]}],["$","h3","9",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"3. Complex property data"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A property listing is not just text and photos. It includes legal description, square footage, zoning, tax history, inspection reports, comps, mortgage details, and 20 other data points."}]]}],["$","p","11",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A generic CRM cannot model this."}]]}],["$","h3","12",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"4. Document-heavy workflows"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Real estate involves tons of documents: purchase agreements, disclosure forms, inspection reports, title documents, HOA docs, financing docs. Managing these is a major part of the job."}]]}],["$","h3","14",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"5. Integration with MLS"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Every agent uses the MLS (Multiple Listing Service) to find properties and list their own. The real estate software needs to integrate with MLS data, not duplicate it."}]]}],["$","h2","16",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"What a Real Estate Software System Needs"}],["$","h3","17",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","chi